Hi again Kevin,
 
Yes, Steve has set up a system that limits the amount of exhibitors in virtually every Category you do…DJ (5), Photobooth (4) and Video (5). He did this to not oversaturate certain categories. He wants to keep a nice shopping environment for Brides so they don’t see just one type of exhibitor category and get burnt out and still provide a competitive environment that is beneficial for every vendor. Too many of one type is bad for everyone. The only drawback is for a select group of Vendors like yourself, who would take 3 of those 14 available spots in one space. We do permit it but there is a premium to be paid.
 
He also told me that you and Jody Amos are good friends and long time associates and you both have a long history with Brocade’s owners Wasim & Shazli.  Jody comes to our shows and we could offer you the same deal we offer him that is a little less than normal.
 
We offer Jody $1399 for one show, 1199 for 2 shows and $999 for 3 or more shows, instead of the Normal $1599 for a Multi-Line exhibitor. I might have a 3 show package I could put together for you  at maybe even less if you’d like me to try to work it out?
